---
alwaysApply: true
---

globs: src/**/*.ts, scripts/**/*.ts, tests/**/*.ts, dashboard/**/*.ts, dashboard/**/*.tsx

Bun-first commands: bun run, bun test.

Strict TS:

No any unless justified and localized.

Prefer explicit domain types and schema validation.

Input safety:

Validate external inputs (CLI args, tool payloads, API payloads) with zod (or your existing schema system).

Error handling:

No silent catches.

Use project logger patterns; wrap errors into domain-specific errors where it improves observability.
